title: The Forest 0.16 & 0.16 Trainer[nosTEAM]
description:
As the lone survivor of a passenger jet crash, you find yourself in a mysterious forest battling to stay alive against a society of cannibalistic mutants. Build, explore, survive in this terrifying first person survival horror simulator.


Launch installer.

Install game.

Once game is installed launch the game.

Play it.

If you want cheats then read on.

Launch The Forest V0.16 Trainer +9 MrAntiFun


To enable cheats you must launch the game first as it just hangs before the plane scene when you launch the cheat menu before launching the game.
